{"thag2.30:0.1":"Theragatha 2.30 ","thag2.30:0.2":"Dukanipata ","thag2.30:0.3":"Tatiyavagga ","thag2.30:0.4":"Kanhadinnattheragatha ","thag2.30:1.1":"“Upasita sappurisa, ","thag2.30:1.2":"suta dhamma abhinhaso; ","thag2.30:1.3":"Sutvana patipajjissam, ","thag2.30:1.4":"anjasam amatogadham. ","thag2.30:2.1":"Bhavaragahatassa me sato, ","thag2.30:2.2":"Bhavarago puna me na vijjati; ","thag2.30:2.3":"Na cahu na ca me bhavissati, ","thag2.30:2.4":"Na ca me etarahi vijjati”ti. ","thag2.30:2.5":"… Kanhadinno thero … ","thag2.30:2.6":"vaggo tatiyo. ","thag2.30:3.0":"Tassuddanam ","thag2.30:3.1":"Uttaro bhaddajitthero, ","thag2.30:3.2":"sobhito valliyo isi; ","thag2.30:3.3":"Vitasoko ca yo thero, ","thag2.30:3.4":"punnamaso ca nandako; ","thag2.30:3.5":"Bharato bharadvajo ca, ","thag2.30:3.6":"kanhadinno mahamuniti. "}